sentences: Park Sun-young (born August 12, 1993), known professionally as Luna, is a South Korean singer, musical actress and television presenter.
She debuted as a member of girl group f(x) in September 2009.
She also starred in the film The Lightning Man's Secret (2015).
In 2016, she released her debut extended play
In September 2019, Luna left SM Entertainment and joined Humap Contents for her future solo activities.
In February 2021, Luna established her own entertainment agency called Grida Entertainment.
Luna was born as Park Sun-young in Seoul, South Korea on August 12, 1993 to a family of classical vocal singers.
